					<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="https://statmodeling.stat.columbia.edu/category/zombies/" rel="category tag">Zombies</a>			</span>
							
										
										<span class="sep"> | </span>
