				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="https://statmodeling.stat.columbia.edu/2022/10/07/les-distributions-a-priori-pour-linference-causale-my-talk-in-paris-tues-11-oct-14h/" title="9:58 am" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2022-10-07T09:58:46-04:00">October 7, 2022 9:58 AM</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://statmodeling.stat.columbia.edu/author/andrew/" title="View all posts by Andrew" rel="author">Andrew</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
